OL,3,CTim Davie and Deborah Turness'
OL,4,Cresignation statements in full
OL,6,FBBC director-general Tim Davie and BBC
OL,7,FNews chief executive Deborah Turness
OL,8,Fhave resigned following a newspaper
OL,9,Freport claiming a Panorama documentary
OL,10,Fmisled viewers by editing a speech by
OL,11,FUS President Donald Trump.
OL,13,FThe controversy centres on a memo from
OL,14,FMichael Prescott, a former external
OL,15,Fadviser to the BBC's editorial
OL,16,Fstandards committee, who raised
OL,17,Fconcerns over how clips of Trump's
OL,18,FJanuary 6, 2021, speech were edited in
OL,19,Fthe Trump: A Second Chance? episode.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
