OL,3,CTim Davie and Deborah Turness'
OL,4,Cresignation statements in full
OL,6,FCritics said the edits made it appear
OL,7,Fhe had told supporters he would walk
OL,8,Fto the US Capitol with them to "fight
OL,9,Flike hell," while removing a section
OL,10,Fwhere he called for a peaceful
OL,11,Fdemonstration.
OL,13,FThe documentary aired the week before
OL,14,Flast year's US election, prompting
OL,15,Faccusations of misleading coverage.
OL,17,FThe BBC is expected to issue an
OL,18,Fapology on Monday over the
OL,19,Fimpartiality concerns.
