OL,3,CTim Davie and Deborah Turness'
OL,4,Cresignation statements in full
OL,6,FBoth announced their departures in
OL,7,Fseparate emails to all BBC staff on
OL,8,FSunday at 18:00.
OL,10,FHere are their resignation emails in
OL,11,Ffull:
OL,13,FI wanted to let you know that I have
OL,14,Fdecided to leave the BBC after 20
OL,15,Fyears. This is entirely my decision,
OL,16,Fand I remain very thankful to the
OL,17,FChair and Board for their unswerving
OL,18,Fand unanimous support throughout my
OL,19,Fentire tenure, including during recent
OL,20,Fdays.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
