OL,4,Cresignation statements in full
OL,6,FI am working through exact timings
OL,7,Fwith the Board to allow for an orderly
OL,8,Ftransition to a successor over the
OL,9,Fcoming months.
OL,11,FI have been reflecting on the very
OL,12,Fintense personal and professional
OL,13,Fdemands of managing this role over
OL,14,Fmany years in these febrile times,
OL,15,Fcombined with the fact that I want to
OL,16,Fgive a successor time to help shape
OL,17,Fthe Charter plans they will be
OL,18,Fdelivering.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
