OL,3,CTim Davie and Deborah Turness'
OL,4,Cresignation statements in full
OL,6,FDespite a hugely competitive market, I
OL,7,Fam proud that the BBC remains the most
OL,8,Ftrusted news brand globally. We have
OL,9,Fcontinued to ensure that it is used by
OL,10,Falmost everyone in the UK as well as
OL,11,Fhundreds of millions of people
OL,12,Fglobally. Despite the inevitable
OL,13,Fissues and challenges, our journalism
OL,14,Fand quality content continues to be
OL,15,Fadmired as a gold standard. Our
OL,16,Ftransition to a digital organisation
OL,17,Fhas been deeply impressive, and our
OL,18,Fthriving commercial businesses are
OL,19,Fadmired globally. Also, our work
OL,20,Ftogether on ensuring that we have the
OL,21,Fright culture has been important and
OL,22,Fmotivating. I could not be more
OL,23,Fimpressed by what you are achieving.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
