OL,3,CTim Davie and Deborah Turness'
OL,4,Cresignation statements in full
OL,6,FI am BBC through and through, having
OL,7,Fspent the last 20 years of my life
OL,8,Fworking for this organisation as
OL,9,FDirector of Marketing, Communications
OL,10,Fand Audiences, Director of Audio and
OL,11,FMusic, acting Director-General and
OL,12,FChief Executive of BBC Studios. I care
OL,13,Fdeeply about it and want it to
OL,14,Fsucceed. That is why I want to create
OL,15,Fthe best conditions and space for a
OL,16,Fnew DG to come in and positively shape
OL,17,Fthe next Royal Charter. I hope that as
OL,18,Fwe move forward, a sensible, calm and
OL,19,Frational public conversation can take
OL,20,Fplace about the next chapter of the
OL,21,FBBC.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
