OL,4,Cresignation statements in full
OL,6,FI have taken the difficult decision
OL,7,Fthat it will no longer be my role to
OL,8,Flead you in the collective vision that
OL,9,Fwe all have: to pursue the truth with
OL,10,Fno agenda.
OL,12,FThe ongoing controversy around the
OL,13,FPanorama on President Trump has
OL,14,Freached a stage where it is causing
OL,15,Fdamage to the BBC ` an institution
OL,16,Fthat I love.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
