OL,3,CTim Davie and Deborah Turness'
OL,4,Cresignation statements in full
OL,6,FAs the CEO of BBC News and Current
OL,7,FAffairs, the buck stops with me - and
OL,8,FI took the decision to offer my
OL,9,Fresignation to the Director-General
OL,10,Flast night.
OL,12,FIn public life leaders need to be
OL,13,Ffully accountable, and that is why I
OL,14,Fam stepping down. While mistakes have
OL,15,Fbeen made, I want to be absolutely
OL,16,Fclear recent allegations that BBC News
OL,17,Fis institutionally biased are wrong.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
