OL,3,CTim Davie and Deborah Turness'
OL,4,Cresignation statements in full
OL,6,FIn a polarised world, BBC News
OL,7,Fjournalism is more vital than ever,
OL,8,Fand I could not be prouder of the work
OL,9,Fthat you do. Together we have bucked
OL,10,Fthe global trend, to grow trust in BBC
OL,11,FNews, and I want to thank you,
OL,12,Fwherever you are in the world, for
OL,13,Fyour courageous work to deliver that.
OL,15,FMy plea to you: please keep the
OL,16,Fcourage to continue our mission. I'm
OL,17,Fonly sorry that I won't be there to
OL,18,Flead and champion your brilliant
OL,19,Fjournalism.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
