OL,6,FIt has been a great privilege to work
OL,7,Fwith you all.
OL,9,FI will now work with Tim to plan an
OL,10,Forderly handover to ensure that my
OL,11,Fdecision to step away causes the least
OL,12,Fdisruption possible to the important
OL,13,Fwork that you do.
OL,15,FWith very best wishes,
